      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully serviced. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement and remains on its original, impeccably maintained suspension geometry. Every factory VIN tag is present, and the exterior retains its original deep luster. This is a mechanically superior, concours-level example of BMW\u2019s analog peak, offering unparalleled tactile feedback and performance.",
